reviews.comment:
(Translated by Google) They can have good sandwiches, good dishes, whatever you want, but the bravas are excessively disastrous, apart from not having brava sauce and putting a mayonnaise of dubious quality on it, the beers are served in small glasses, the first and last time we come to this place , in addition to the arrogance of the waiter saying that they have been doing the bravas like this for 20 years and nobody ever said anything ... In short, we will not return.

(Original)
Pueden tener buenos bocadillos, buenos platos lo que quieras pero las bravas son excesivamente nefastas, a parte de no llevar salsa brava y ponerle una mayonesa de dudosa calidad, las cañas te las sirven en copas pequeñas, primera y última vez que venimos a este lugar, además de la prepotencia del camarero diciendo que llevan 20 años haciendo las bravas así y nunca nadie dijo nada... En fin no volveremos.
reviews.name: accounts/107486734643006837997/locations/10693761007558595766/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNPLUxLdzN3RRAB
